@startuml

title Plan-Write-Error

'skinparam actorStyle awesome

skinparam borderColor #000000
skinparam backgroundColor #f5f5f5
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 10
skinparam defaultFontName "Arial"
skinparam defaultFontSize 14
skinparam defaultFontColor #000000
skinparam HyperlinkColor #0000EE
skinparam HyperlinkUnderline false
skinparam BoxPadding 20
skinparam BoxBorderColor #555555

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #e0e5f0-#d1d9e6
  BorderColor #8b95a5
  BorderThickness 1
  RoundCorner 0
  Padding 6
  FontColor #111827
  Shadowing false
}

skinparam sequence {
  ParticipantBorderColor #555555
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #ffffff
  ParticipantFontColor #000000
  ParticipantFontSize 14
  ParticipantPadding 20
  ArrowColor #111827
  ArrowThickness 1
  ArrowFontColor #000000
  ArrowFontSize 13
  GroupBorderColor #111827
  GroupBackgroundColor #eef2ff
  GroupBorderThickness 2
}

!define COLOR_GDA_1    #15608280
!define COLOR_GDA_2    #96607D80
!define COLOR_PATIENT  #196B2480
!define COLOR_APO      #0F9ED590
!define COLOR_EMED_FA  #e97232bd
!define COLOR_E_REZEPT #cd3732a9

!define COLOR_OK       #0F9ED525
!define COLOR_ERROR    #E9713235

actor GDA_1 as "GDA 1" COLOR_GDA_1
participant eMed_FA as "e-Med FA" COLOR_EMED_FA
actor GDA_2 as "GDA 2" COLOR_GDA_2

autonumber
 
== Plan-Read durch GDA 1 ==

GDA_1 -> eMed_FA: POST $plan-read
activate GDA_1 COLOR_GDA_1

activate eMed_FA COLOR_EMED_FA
eMed_FA -> GDA_1: Collection Bundle + ETag "123"
deactivate eMed_FA

note over GDA_1
GDA 1 bearbeitet Medikationsplan
(Einträge hinzufügen/ändern/entfernen)
end note

== Plan-Read durch GDA 2 ==

GDA_2 -> eMed_FA: POST $plan-read
activate GDA_2 COLOR_GDA_2

activate eMed_FA COLOR_EMED_FA

eMed_FA -> GDA_2: Collection Bundle + ETag "123"
deactivate eMed_FA

note over GDA_2
GDA 2 bearbeitet Medikationsplan
(Einträge hinzufügen/ändern/entfernen)
end note

== Plan-Write durch GDA 2 ==

GDA_2 -> eMed_FA: POST $plan-write (Transaction\nBundle + ETag "123")

activate eMed_FA COLOR_EMED_FA
eMed_FA -> eMed_FA: ETag "123" im Header ==\nETag der Fachanwendung "123"
eMed_FA --> GDA_2: OK 
deactivate GDA_2

note over eMed_FA
Medikationsplan wurde durch GDA 2 aktualisiert.
end note

deactivate eMed_FA

== Plan-Write-Error für GDA 1 ==

GDA_1 -> eMed_FA: POST $plan-write (Transaction Bundle + ETag "123")

activate eMed_FA COLOR_EMED_FA
eMed_FA -> eMed_FA: ETag im Header "123" stimmt nicht\nmit ETag der Fachanwendung\nüberein, da er bereits zum Schreiben\nverwendet wurde
note over eMed_FA
Fachanwendung lehnt Speichern ab
end note
eMed_FA --> GDA_1: Fehler (Konflikt)
deactivate GDA_1
note over eMed_FA, GDA_1
Speichern des Medikationsplans wurde abgelehnt, 
der GDA 1 muss ein neues Plan-Read ausführen.
end note

deactivate eMed_FA

@enduml